{"tid":1107382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國工人「吊」50米電塔睡覺 網友熱議","createTime":"2019-04-15T08:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T09:28:40.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"77a8f4c0240e65f1d14de619be3f9081969899a8","tid":1107382,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/04/Unknown-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FUnknown-600x400.jpg&h=5f7602b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2019年04月15日訊】中國人有午睡的習慣，即使身處特殊情況也不例外。但近日幾名中國電力工人在50米高的電塔上睡覺的視頻卻引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n近日，一段「中國工人在50米電塔上睡著」的視頻在YouTube走紅，目前該視頻的觀看次數已經超過16.8萬次。 <br />\n<br />\n視頻中顯示，一座50米高的電塔上，幾名電力工人或者吊在繩索上，或者依靠在鐵架上閉眼休息。視頻中還顯示工人休息的地方距離地面很遠。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這段視頻源自中國電力工人小蔣上傳在「快手」的視頻，地點是在湖南郴州。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uSYdq0fLL9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuSYdq0fLL9A&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=925ce4eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uSYdq0fLL9A</a><br />\n<br />\n他表示，工作時最高要爬百米高的電塔，因為上下塔很累，一般上去了就不輕易下來。所以大家只有吃飯時才會下來，短暫休息只能在塔上。<br />\n<br />\n這位工人坦言：「剛開始也害怕，但高空作業有多重保護，包括二保繩和安全帶等，習慣以後就不害怕了。<br />\n<br />\n這段視頻被轉發到YouTube網站後，令大批外國網友心驚膽戰：「我看得的腿都軟了，向這些工人致敬。」「我的手心冒汗」，「想像一下如果夢到掉下，身體猛然彈起（會是怎樣的危險）」。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友說，「這是不是就是中國人習慣的午睡，即使在塔尖也不例外」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友稱讚中國人的勤勞，指這些人才是中國的經濟發展的根本所在。 <br />\n<br />\n也有網友認為，這顯示他們過度工作（overworked）。<br />\n<br />\n這些工人也不禁讓人想起四川涼山懸崖村的攀爬雲梯上學的視頻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vRh4fRm4q-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvRh4fRm4q-8&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=1fd83205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vRh4fRm4q-8</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年，媒體爆光了涼山彝族自治州昭覺縣支爾莫鄉阿土勒爾村的生活現狀。在這個海拔1400多米，與地面垂直距離約800米的村子，村民進出都需要順著懸崖斷續攀爬17條藤梯，村裡的兒童上學都需要攀懸崖，幾乎垂直上下的簡易繩索讓人看的膽戰心驚，曾經多人因為攀懸崖被摔死。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：林詩遠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/4/14/n11186361.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F4%2F14%2Fn11186361.htm&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=95349b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/4/14/n11186361.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stat.ameba.jp/user_images/20161029/05/everytime-777/af/f6/j/o0990055613784367872.jpg?caw=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstat.ameba.jp%2Fuser_images%2F20161029%2F05%2Feverytime-777%2Faf%2Ff6%2Fj%2Fo0990055613784367872.jpg%3Fcaw%3D800&h=ec11a7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60fa55816a46ff8e455542144f238c109212445","tid":1107382,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"jojo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3513aee2305ece5aee3501256f2af9bb6b7230f6","tid":1107382,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"這是替身攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d754952ebf93298f7b6022b60b5fc946cbf277","tid":1107382,"uid":36010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"似電撚死咗多啲"},{"pid":"c74e81ff8db332a4b664ca1491cf44c9c5f9b29d","tid":1107382,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e8d634b96fd2228c6a0dbb4bfab21b68b9477e","tid":1107382,"uid":32691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"咁猛太陽都訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b05bd50d955fd24873e213244682154c93b8275","tid":1107382,"uid":18948,"like